If a defendant is charged with a misdemeanor offense and remains hospitalized two (2)
years after the date of arrest, then the reporting obligations of this subsection (c) must
continue until the defendant is discharged.
SECTION 3. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 52-6-102, is amended by deleting
subdivision (e)(2).
SECTION 4. This act takes effect July 1, 2025, the public welfare requiring it.
